rl.photoviewer.model

Class MapDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • rl.photoviewer.model.MapDataManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapData

    public class MapDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements MapData
    The MapDataManager maintains all the data which is needed for map display and position marking. Besides a map image, at least two reference points are needed which map image positions (in pixel) to latitude/longitude values. The manager also maintains a lookup-table for previously used map files which can be stored and loaded.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
